      <section aria-labelledby="photo-guidelines-title">
        <h2 id="photo-guidelines-title" class="section-title">Profile Photo Guidelines</h2>
        <p>For a clear, professional result, please follow these when taking your photo:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Background:</strong> Plain, light-colored wall; no patterns or wrinkled sheets.</li>
          <li><strong>Camera quality:</strong> Modern phone or camera; no screenshots or photos of photos.</li>
          <li><strong>Position:</strong> Face the camera straight on, head centered, shoulders visible.</li>
          <li><strong>Lighting:</strong> Even light on your face; avoid strong shadows and bright backlight.</li>
          <li><strong>Appearance:</strong> Neat clothing that contrasts with the background; no sunglasses/tinted lenses.</li>
          <li><strong>Framing:</strong> Full face and tops of shoulders, with a bit of space above your head.</li>
          <li><strong>Expression:</strong> Neutral or slight smile, both eyes open.</li>
          <li>
            <strong>File:</strong> Upload the original JPG/PNG to
            <a href="https://cryptgeon.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">cryptgeon.org</a>
            and paste the link below.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

